title: Thou - Heathen (2014) - 320kbps
description:
'Thou' is a Sludge/Drone/Doom Metal band hailing from Louisiana. The band has been active since early 2005 and have released a rather long catalog of music since. This is one of their most recent full length releases. This record is absolutely crushing, dark and atmospheric, definitely something you should have in your music library.

Tracklist:

1. Free Will
2. Dawn (Interlude 1)
3. Feral Faun
4. Into the Marshland
5. Clarity (Interlude 3)
6. At the Foot of Mt. Driskill
7. In Defiance of the Sages
8. Take Off Your Skin and Dance in Your Bones 
(Interlude 4)
9. Immortality Dictates
10. Ode to Physical Pain
